hat is around this particular part. The wide-ranging debate relates to the readings. The Committee stage relates to the analysis of the parts that are before the Committee. There has been quite a bit of leniency displayed so far, for members to be able to do that. I am giving you an indication, as I have on previous tours of duty in respect of this particular bill, that we are going to keep it tight.</p></div></body>
