es live here on one side of this House. We will keep working for affordable housing. </p><p class="a">Thank you very much. This might be a frivolous contribution, but my heart has been in this process, along with everyone else's. Thank you to everyone who put up a constructive solution to actually make this piece of legislation worth having. The fact that the Government members voted it all down—let that be on their own consciences. "The whole world is watching" notes the <em>Guardian</em>. Good night.</p></div></body>
